# Shape Toolbar Mapping

This rule documents the shape toolbar found in [app/index.tsx](mdc:app/index.tsx).

**Shape types and their icons**

- rectangle → ▭
- circle → ●
- triangle → ▲
- diamond → ◆
- star → ★
- hexagon → ⬡

**Default element sizes**

- rectangle: 100 × 100
- star & hexagon: 70 × 70
- all others: 60 × 60

These guidelines help the AI understand how elements are created, rendered, and manipulated on the canvas.

